 away from his love Patricia Neal. But things take an unexpected 

 turn when Neal marries a newspaper tycoon who wages a campaign 

 against Cooper?s novel ideas. The screen adaptation of Ayn 

 Rand?s novel is a journey into the deep bond shared by the 

 lovers. 

 THE SHOW

 (GD Birla Sabhagar, 7 pm, November 20) l After debuting 

 on the Calcutta stage with Crossings early this year, 

 Ranan is ready with its second production. The dance drama, 

 based on Girish Karnad?s play, has been conceived and executed 

 by Vikram Iyengar. 

